    public static class PreferencesDlg.DefaultPreferencePanel

implements PreferencePanel, java.awt.event.ActionListener
    PreferencePanel groups a number of preferences.

    Use @link{PreferencePanel.builder()} to create one. You can use the chained .xxxField() methods to add the preferences that you want to edit, with a description.
